name: Rotten Fruit
category: Debris
footprint: 1x1
facing: no
shadow: no
blocks_light: no
height: 0.1
placement: floor
room_types: shrine-roadside, peasant-hovel, cabin-abandoned, cellar, alley, dock-warehouse, sewer
typical_count: few
clusters_with: moldy-bread, bread-crust, fly-swarm, scat-pile, dropped-apple
notes: Rotting apple or fruit on the floor — collapsed brown, mold patches, flies buzzing around.
